    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single loading rate; risk accepted on the basis of strong inter-laboratory reproducibility (CV < 5% across both labs) and robust mesh convergence evidence. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and APD < 10% pre-specified acceptance criteria. Model credibility is sufficient for Medium assurance level at Model Risk Level 3.",
